criteria.driver_alignment:
DISCOVER — defined the objective and decision metrics (NPV, IRR, payback) guiding the analysis;  
IMPLEMENT/REPRESENT — laid out FCF formula, inputs (WACC, life, capex, depreciation, taxes, terminal value) and computed NPV/IRR/payback;  
REFLECT — interpreted results, ran sensitivity tests (revenue and WACC), and stated the accept/reject recommendation with contingencies.
